<p>Below are various examples of bullying situation you could use for this exercise. But remember, you are the experts! You are encouraged to come up with your own examples of bullying situation. Examples that are real and relevant to the current group will always be most effective. Remember, an effective example will be realistic and factual, but will make it clear that the bullying behavior in the example is unacceptable.</p> 
